      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Brett Welch was appointed Legal Director at the Department for Transport in January 2018, having been the Deputy Legal Director for 16 months prior to that.</p>

<p>Previous roles have involved advising HM Treasury and the Department for Education, as well as time spent in what are now HM Revenue & Customs and the National Crime Agency.</p>

</div>
      </section>

